The [[Bayer designation]] '''Theta Sagittarii''' ('''θ&nbsp;Sagittarii''') is shared by two [[star]]s, '''θ<sup>1</sup> Sagittarii''' and '''θ<sup>2</sup> Sagittarii''', in the [[constellation]] [[Sagittarius (constellation)|Sagittarius]]. The pair are separated by 0.58° in the sky.
